messages.message:
Hi all, Sharing an update to the state of a few apps in terms of beta-fying and deprecating:
• Redactor becomes a beta app. Capability is needed, but not the app.
• OCR becomes a beta app, and can be brought back once functionality is improved
• Cluster will be deprecated
• Doc Diff will be deprecated
Eng Owner doc (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ENG/pages/925762121/Eng+Owners) has been updated, and JIRA  (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/PX-986)for tracking the work.
